{"type":null,"faqId":38473,"title":"播放音乐","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.19722222in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p8{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.td1{width:0.82708335in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.td2{width:4.6854167in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.r1{keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125314\" style=\"width:0.24305555in;height:0.1875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“音乐”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">选择一个类别。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击要播放的音乐。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击正在播放的音乐，进入播放主界面，可进行更多操作。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125315\" style=\"width:3.0in;height:3.0in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125316\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p5\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n      </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">左右滑动可在专辑封面、播放列表和歌词之间进行切换。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      <p class=\"p5\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n      </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击可进行更多操作，如调节播放音量、打开选项菜单等。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125317\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">将歌曲裁剪成小片段，并可设置为铃声。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125318\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">控制音乐播放。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125319\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p4\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">打开菜单进行更多操作。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125320\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"p6\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 10.5pt; \">播放音乐时，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125321\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-var